"Fix moving around"
    nnoremap m h|
    xnoremap m h|
    onoremap m h|

    nnoremap n j|
    xnoremap n j|
    onoremap n j|

    nnoremap e k|
    xnoremap e k|
    onoremap e k|

    nnoremap i l|
    xnoremap i l|
    onoremap i l|



"Fix Insert and Undo"
    nnoremap u i
    xnoremap u i

    nnoremap l u


"Jump to bottom of row"
    nnoremap I L
    xnoremap I L
    onoremap I L


"Change Case"
    xnoremap l u
    xnoremap L U

